<div class="story"><p>If mountain living is on the home shopping must have list but being close to the ocean would be a dream come true, then the community of Hickory Ridge in Kitty Hawk might be a great compromise to consider. Tucked away in the heart of <a href="http://www.nccoastalreserve.net/web/crp/kitty-hawk-woods" title="Kitty Hawk Woods">Kitty Hawk Woods</a>, the maritime forest environment of Hickory Ridge is just minutes away from the beach. Hickory Ridge is located at the end of Kitty Hawk Road across from <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/kitty-hawk-landing.asp" title="Kitty Hawk Landing">Kitty Hawk Landing</a>. </p><p><a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/hickory-ridge-covenants.pdf" title="Hickory Ridge Covenants">Hickory Ridge Covenants</a> <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/hickory-ridge-amendment.pdf" title="Hickory Ridge Amended Covenants">Hickory Ridge Amended Covenants</a>   - - - <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/Covenant-Disclaimer.asp" target="_blank"><b>    *</b></a></p>
